he implications of our results for the thermal evolution\nand multiphase structure of galaxy halos, groups and clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2019 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Feb 2020 22:54:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-24"}
