ively, it could result from\nlocally anisotropic synchrotron emissivities. Multi-epoch and polarimetric\nresults from the EHT will be essential to verify the theoretically expected\nalignment of the BH spin with the large-scale jet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2019 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Sep 2019 09:59:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Oct 2019 12:50:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 31 Dec 2019 09:34:12 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 15:43:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-01"}
