rm an asymptotic analysis of\nthe governing system as two (small) relaxation parameters approach zero\nseparately and simultaneously. Corresponding well-posedness and regularity\nresults are established for the respective cases; in particular, we give a\ndetailed discussion which assumptions on the admissible nonlinearities have to\nbe postulated in each of the occurring cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2019 11:35:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-29"}
