over-critical regime where they rotate collectively around the considered\nhome. We additionally elaborate the overdamped Smoluchowski-limit for the\nensemble.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2019 11:51:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
