esults can be used to understand the\ndynamic behavior of any zoonosis with intermediate hosts and assist efforts to\nprotect public health.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Aug 2019 15:47:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
